+                    <h1 class="modulename">
+narrative_engine    </h1>
+
+                        <div class="docstring"><p>Psychological Narrative Engine - Multi-NPC Conversation Engine</p>
+
+<p>A Fallout-style psychological narrative engine where:</p>
+
+<ul>
+<li>Player choices are visible and structured (node/choice tree)</li>
+<li>NPC responses are generated via the BDI+LLM pipeline</li>
+<li>Scenarios are NPC-agnostic; NPC individuality is injected at runtime</li>
+<li>Multiple NPCs can participate independently in the same scenario</li>
+<li>Routing between nodes is DYNAMIC: driven by NPC BDI state + player_relation</li>
+</ul>
+
+<p>Author: Jerome Bawa (original), refactor by AI assistant</p>
+</div>
