+            <div class="pdoc-code codehilite"><pre><span></span><span id="NarrativeEngine-29"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-29"><span class="linenos"> 29</span></a><span class="k">class</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">NarrativeEngine</span><span class="p">:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-30"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-30"><span class="linenos"> 30</span></a><span class="w">    </span><span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-31"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-31"><span class="linenos"> 31</span></a><span class="sd">    High-level orchestrator for Fallout-style conversations using pne&#39;s BDI engine.</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-32"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-32"><span class="linenos"> 32</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-33"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-33"><span class="linenos"> 33</span></a><span class="sd">    Key difference from traditional choice-based systems:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-34"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-34"><span class="linenos"> 34</span></a><span class="sd">    - Choices no longer have next_node hardcoded</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-35"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-35"><span class="linenos"> 35</span></a><span class="sd">    - After a choice is processed, each NPC&#39;s state is evaluated against</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-36"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-36"><span class="linenos"> 36</span></a><span class="sd">      the CURRENT node&#39;s transitions to determine where that NPC goes next</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-37"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-37"><span class="linenos"> 37</span></a><span class="sd">    - Different NPCs can end up on different nodes after the same player choice</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-38"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-38"><span class="linenos"> 38</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-39"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-39"><span class="linenos"> 39</span></a><span class="sd">    Workflow:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-40"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-40"><span class="linenos"> 40</span></a><span class="sd">    1. Load NPCs (personality, beliefs, world state)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-41"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-41"><span class="linenos"> 41</span></a><span class="sd">    2. Load scenario (nodes, choices, transitions - NPC-agnostic)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-42"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-42"><span class="linenos"> 42</span></a><span class="sd">    3. Start session (inject NPCs into scenario)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-43"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-43"><span class="linenos"> 43</span></a><span class="sd">    4. Process player choices:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-44"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-44"><span class="linenos"> 44</span></a><span class="sd">       - Parse choice into PlayerDialogueInput</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-45"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-45"><span class="linenos"> 45</span></a><span class="sd">       - Run through each NPC&#39;s DialogueProcessor (BDI + LLM)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-46"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-46"><span class="linenos"> 46</span></a><span class="sd">       - Evaluate transitions against each NPC&#39;s updated state</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-47"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-47"><span class="linenos"> 47</span></a><span class="sd">       - Route each NPC to appropriate next node</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-48"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-48"><span class="linenos"> 48</span></a><span class="sd">    5. Export rich conversation logs</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-49"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-49"><span class="linenos"> 49</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-50"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-50"><span class="linenos"> 50</span></a><span class="sd">    Attributes:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-51"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-51"><span class="linenos"> 51</span></a><span class="sd">        use_ollama: Whether to use Ollama for LLM generation</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-52"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-52"><span class="linenos"> 52</span></a><span class="sd">        ollama_url: URL for Ollama API endpoint</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-53"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-53"><span class="linenos"> 53</span></a><span class="sd">        scenarios: Dict of loaded scenarios (scenario_id -&gt; scenario data)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-54"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-54"><span class="linenos"> 54</span></a><span class="sd">        npcs: Dict of loaded NPCs (npc_id -&gt; NPCModel)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-55"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-55"><span class="linenos"> 55</span></a><span class="sd">        sessions: Dict of active conversation sessions (session_id -&gt; ConversationSession)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-56"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-56"><span class="linenos"> 56</span></a><span class="sd">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-57"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-57"><span class="linenos"> 57</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-58"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-58"><span class="linenos"> 58</span></a>    <span class="k">def</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="fm">__init__</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">use_ollama</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">bool</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ollama_url</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">str</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;http://localhost:11434&quot;</span><span class="p">):</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-59"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-59"><span class="linenos"> 59</span></a><span class="w">        </span><span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-60"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-60"><span class="linenos"> 60</span></a><span class="sd">        Initialize the narrative engine.</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-61"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-61"><span class="linenos"> 61</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-62"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-62"><span class="linenos"> 62</span></a><span class="sd">        Args:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-63"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-63"><span class="linenos"> 63</span></a><span class="sd">            use_ollama: Whether to use Ollama for LLM-based response generation</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-64"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-64"><span class="linenos"> 64</span></a><span class="sd">            ollama_url: URL of the Ollama API endpoint</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-65"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-65"><span class="linenos"> 65</span></a><span class="sd">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-66"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-66"><span class="linenos"> 66</span></a>        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">use_ollama</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">use_ollama</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-67"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-67"><span class="linenos"> 67</span></a>        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ollama_url</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ollama_url</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-68"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-68"><span class="linenos"> 68</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-69"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-69"><span class="linenos"> 69</span></a>        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">scenarios</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">Dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Any</span><span class="p">]]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-70"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-70"><span class="linenos"> 70</span></a>        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">npcs</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">Dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NPCModel</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-71"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-71"><span class="linenos"> 71</span></a>        <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sessions</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">Dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ConversationSession</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-72"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-72"><span class="linenos"> 72</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-73"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-73"><span class="linenos"> 73</span></a>    <span class="nd">@staticmethod</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-74"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-74"><span class="linenos"> 74</span></a>    <span class="k">def</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">_format_with_npc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">npc_name</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-75"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-75"><span class="linenos"> 75</span></a><span class="w">        </span><span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-76"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-76"><span class="linenos"> 76</span></a><span class="sd">        Replace simple parsewords in scenario text.</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-77"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-77"><span class="linenos"> 77</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-78"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-78"><span class="linenos"> 78</span></a><span class="sd">        Currently supported:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-79"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-79"><span class="linenos"> 79</span></a><span class="sd">          {{NPC_NAME}} -&gt; concrete NPC model name (e.g. &#39;Moses&#39;, &#39;Taylor&#39;)</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-80"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-80"><span class="linenos"> 80</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-81"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-81"><span class="linenos"> 81</span></a><span class="sd">        Args:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-82"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-82"><span class="linenos"> 82</span></a><span class="sd">            text: Text containing parsewords</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-83"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-83"><span class="linenos"> 83</span></a><span class="sd">            npc_name: Name of the NPC to substitute</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-84"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-84"><span class="linenos"> 84</span></a>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-85"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-85"><span class="linenos"> 85</span></a><span class="sd">        Returns:</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-86"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-86"><span class="linenos"> 86</span></a><span class="sd">            Text with parsewords replaced by actual NPC data</span>
+</span><span id="NarrativeEngine-87"><a href="#NarrativeEngine-87"><span class="linenos"> 87</span></a><span class="sd">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
