+            <div class="docstring"><p>Add a dialogue exchange to the visible history log.</p>
+
+<p>This creates a Fallout-style conversation log with speaker,
+text, and optional metadata (thoughts, desires, intentions).</p>
+
+<p>Args:
+    speaker: Name of the speaker ("Player", NPC name, or "Narrator")
+    text: The dialogue text
+    metadata: Optional dict containing:
+        - thought: Internal thought reaction
+        - desire: Current desire state
+        - intention: Behavioral intention
+        - interaction_outcome: Outcome data for this exchange</p>
+</div>
+
