aram\">\t<span class=\"n\">player_skills</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">player_input</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">PlayerSkillSet</span><span class=\"p\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">None</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.get_node": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.get_node", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NarrativeEngine.get_node", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Get a node from the session's scenario.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    session: Current conversation session\n    node_id: ID of the node to retrieve</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Node dict if found, None otherwise</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"bp\">self</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">node_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.get_available_choices": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.get_available_choices", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NarrativeEngine.get_available_choices", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Get all available player choices at a given node.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    session: Current conversation session\n    node_id: ID of the node to get choices from</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    List of choice dicts with index, choice_id, text, and raw data</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"bp\">self</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">node_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.apply_choice": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.apply_choice", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NarrativeEngine.apply_choice", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Apply a single player choice (by index) to all active NPCs.</p>\n\n<p>Flow per NPC:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Parse choice \u2192 PlayerDialogueInput</li>\n<li>Run through DialogueProcessor (BDI + LLM)</li>\n<li>Evaluate current node's transitions against updated NPC state</li>\n<li>Route NPC to the resolved target node (or stay if no match)</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>This is where the dynamic routing happens: same choice, potentially\ndifferent outcomes for each NPC based on their internal state.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    session: Current conversation session\n    node_id: ID of the current node\n    choice_index: Index of the player's choice (1-based)</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Dict mapping npc_id to {context, resolved_node}</p>\n\n<p>Raises:\n    ValueError: If node_id is invalid or choice_index is out of range</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"bp\">self</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">node_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">choice_index</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">int</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.is_session_complete": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.is_session_complete", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NarrativeEngine.is_session_complete", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Check if the conversation session is complete.</p>\n\n<p>Session ends when all NPCs have reached terminal states.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    session: The conversation session to check</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    True if all NPCs are complete, False otherwise</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"bp\">self</span>, </span><span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"nb\">bool</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.export_session_log": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NarrativeEngine.export_session_log", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NarrativeEngine.export_session_log", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Export a rich, per-NPC log backed by each NPC's ConversationModel.</p>\n\n<p>The exported JSON contains:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Scenario metadata</li>\n<li>Player choice log</li>\n<li>Per-NPC data:\n<ul>\n<li>Full conversation model (BDI state trajectory)</li>\n<li>Choices made by player</li>\n<li>Visible conversation history</li>\n<li>Terminal outcome</li>\n<li>Final NPC state</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Args:\n    session: The conversation session to export\n    filepath: Path to write the JSON log file</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"bp\">self</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationSession</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">filepath</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"kc\">None</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>A running conversation session for a single scenario and one or more NPCs.</p>\n\n<p>The session manages:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Scenario structure (NPC-agnostic nodes, choices, transitions)</li>\n<li>Multiple NPC states (each with independent BDI processing)</li>\n<li>Shared player choice log (visible conversation history)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Key Design:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Scenario is NPC-agnostic (same structure for any NPC)</li>\n<li>Each NPC has its own BDI/LLM pipeline and memory</li>\n<li>Player choices are shared across all NPCs</li>\n<li>Routing is resolved per-NPC via TransitionResolver</li>\n<li>Different NPCs can diverge to different nodes after same player choice</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Attributes:\n    scenario_id: Unique identifier for the scenario\n    scenario: Complete scenario data structure\n    npc_states: Dict mapping npc_id to NPCConversationState\n    player_choice_log: Global log of player choices (independent of NPC internals)</p>\n"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.__init__": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.__init__", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.__init__", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">scenario_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">scenario</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">npc_states</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NPCConversationState</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">player_choice_log</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">factory</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span></span>)</span>"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.scenario_id": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.scenario_id", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.scenario_id", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": str"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.scenario": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.scenario", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.scenario", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": Dict[str, Any]"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.npc_states": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.npc_states", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.npc_states", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": Dict[str, narrative_engine.session.NPCConversationState]"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.player_choice_log": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.player_choice_log", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.player_choice_log", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": List[Dict[str, Any]]"}, "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.active_npcs": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ConversationSession.active_npcs", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ConversationSession.active_npcs", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Get all NPCs that are still active in the conversation.</p>\n\n<p>An NPC is active if their conversation hasn't reached a terminal state.</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    List of NPCConversationState objects for active NPCs</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"bp\">self</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NPCConversationState</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>Per-NPC conversation state inside a shared scenario.</p>\n\n<p>Each NPC participating in a scenario has its own independent state:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>DialogueProcessor: Manages BDI (Belief-Desire-Intention) processing</li>\n<li>Current node: Where this NPC is in the scenario graph</li>\n<li>History: Complete transcript of exchanges with this NPC</li>\n<li>Terminal outcome: Final result if conversation has ended</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This allows multiple NPCs to diverge to different paths in the same\nscenario based on their individual personalities and the player's\ninteractions with each one.</p>\n\n<p>Attributes:\n    npc_id: Unique identifier for this NPC\n    npc: The NPC model containing personality, beliefs, and world state\n    processor: DialogueProcessor handling BDI pipeline for this NPC\n    scenario_id: ID of the scenario this conversation is part of\n    current_node: Current position in the scenario graph (default: \"start\")\n    is_complete: Whether this NPC's conversation has ended\n    terminal_outcome: Final outcome data if conversation ended\n    history: Fallout-style visible log of all exchanges\n    choices_made: List of choice IDs the player has made with this NPC</p>\n"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.__init__": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.__init__", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.__init__", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">npc_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">npc</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">PNE_Models</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NPCModel</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">processor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">processor</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">DialogueProcessor</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">scenario_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">current_node</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;start&#39;</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">is_complete</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">bool</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">False</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">terminal_outcome</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">None</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">history</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">factory</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">choices_made</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">factory</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span></span>)</span>"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.npc_id": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.npc_id", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.npc_id", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": str"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.npc": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.npc", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.npc", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": PNE_Models.NPCModel"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.processor": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.processor", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.processor", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": pne.processor.DialogueProcessor"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.scenario_id": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.scenario_id", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.scenario_id", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": str"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.current_node": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.current_node", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.current_node", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": str", "default_value": "&#x27;start&#x27;"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.is_complete": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.is_complete", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.is_complete", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": bool", "default_value": "False"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.terminal_outcome": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.terminal_outcome", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.terminal_outcome", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": Optional[Dict[str, Any]]", "default_value": "None"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.history": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.history", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.history", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": List[Dict[str, Any]]"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.choices_made": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.choices_made", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.choices_made", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "annotation": ": List[str]"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.conversation_model": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.conversation_model", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.conversation_model", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Get the underlying ConversationModel from the DialogueProcessor.</p>\n\n<p>The ConversationModel tracks the full BDI state trajectory:\nbeliefs, desires, intentions, and emotional responses over time.</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    ConversationModel instance containing the conversation state</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"bp\">self</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">conversation</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ConversationModel</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.turn_count": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.turn_count", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.turn_count", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p>Get the current turn count for this NPC's conversation.</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Number of conversation turns completed</p>\n", "annotation": ": int"}, "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.add_exchange": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.NPCConversationState.add_exchange", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "NPCConversationState.add_exchange", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Add a dialogue exchange to the visible history log.</p>\n\n<p>This creates a Fallout-style conversation log with speaker,\ntext, and optional metadata (thoughts, desires, intentions).</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    speaker: Name of the speaker (\"Player\", NPC name, or \"Narrator\")\n    text: The dialogue text\n    metadata: Optional dict containing:\n        - thought: Internal thought reaction\n        - desire: Current desire state\n        - intention: Behavioral intention\n        - interaction_outcome: Outcome data for this exchange</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"bp\">self</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">speaker</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">text</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">metadata</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"kc\">None</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"kc\">None</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>Loads generic, NPC-independent scenario JSON.</p>\n\n<p>Scenarios define the conversation flow without being tied to specific NPCs.\nNPC personality and state are injected at runtime during session creation.</p>\n\n<p>Methods:\n    load_scenario: Load scenario from JSON file\n    get_node: Retrieve a specific node by ID\n    parse_npc_intent: Parse high-level NPC intent for the scenario\n    parse_npc_role: Parse NPC role metadata (display name, etc.)\n    parse_player_input: Convert choice JSON to PlayerDialogueInput\n    parse_outcome_index: Build OutcomeIndex from choice metadata</p>\n"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.load_scenario": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.load_scenario", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.load_scenario", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Load a scenario from a JSON file.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    filepath: Path to the scenario JSON file</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Dict containing the complete scenario data structure</p>\n\n<p>Raises:\n    FileNotFoundError: If the scenario file doesn't exist\n    json.JSONDecodeError: If the file contains invalid JSON</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">filepath</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.get_node": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.get_node", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.get_node", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Retrieve a specific node from the scenario by its ID.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    scenario: The loaded scenario dictionary\n    node_id: The unique identifier for the node to retrieve</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Dict containing the node data, or None if not found</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">scenario</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>, </span><span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">node_id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_intent": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_intent", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_intent", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Parse scenario-defined high-level intent for NPCs.</p>\n\n<p>This intent is NPC-agnostic and gets combined with each NPC's\nindividual personality during runtime.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    data: Dict containing intent fields (baseline_belief, long_term_desire, etc.)</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    NPCIntent object with the parsed intent data</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">intent</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NPCIntent</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_role": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_role", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.parse_npc_role", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Parse lightweight role metadata for how the NPC is presented.</p>\n\n<p>This is NPC-agnostic; it just names the 'role' (e.g., 'Door Guard')\nwithout tying it to a specific NPC's personality.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    data: Dict containing role information</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Dict with role metadata (display_name, etc.)</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_player_input": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_player_input", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.parse_player_input", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Convert a choice JSON blob into structured player input.</p>\n\n<p>Parses all the linguistic and tonal components of a player choice,\nincluding language art, authority/diplomacy/empathy/manipulation tones,\nand contextual references.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    choice_data: Dict containing choice text and metadata</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    PlayerDialogueInput object ready for processing by DialogueProcessor</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">choice_data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">player_input</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">PlayerDialogueInput</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_outcome_index": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.ScenarioLoader.parse_outcome_index", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "ScenarioLoader.parse_outcome_index", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Build an OutcomeIndex from choice metadata.</p>\n\n<p>NPC-agnostic: defines <em>potential</em> micro- and terminal outcomes.\nThe DialogueProcessor + NPC state decide which ones actually trigger.</p>\n\n<p>Terminal outcomes are now resolved at the NODE level via transitions,\nnot per-choice. The terminal_outcomes list in choices is typically empty.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    choice_data: Dict containing choice outcomes metadata</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    OutcomeIndex with all potential interaction and terminal outcomes</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">choice_data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">pne</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">outcomes</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">OutcomeIndex</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "TransitionResolver", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>Evaluates a node's transition list against live NPC state to determine\nwhich node to route to next.</p>\n\n<p>Transitions are evaluated in order \u2014 first match wins.\nThis is where the scenario becomes truly NPC-agnostic: same choices,\ndifferent NPC states, different paths.</p>\n\n<p>The resolver supports simple expression evaluation for transition conditions,\nincluding:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>player_relation: The NPC's relationship with the player</li>\n<li>turn_count: Number of conversation turns so far</li>\n<li>Basic comparison operators: ==, !=, &lt;, &gt;, &lt;=, &gt;=, and, or</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Example transition conditions:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\"player_relation &gt; 0.5\"</li>\n<li>\"turn_count &gt;= 3\"</li>\n<li>\"player_relation &lt; 0 and turn_count &gt; 1\"</li>\n</ul>\n"}, "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.SAFE_NAMES": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.SAFE_NAMES", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "TransitionResolver.SAFE_NAMES", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "{&#x27;player_relation&#x27;, &#x27;turn_count&#x27;}"}, "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.resolve": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.resolve", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "TransitionResolver.resolve", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Walk the transition list and return the target node_id for the first\ncondition that evaluates to True.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    transitions: List of transition dicts, each containing:\n        - condition: String expression to evaluate (e.g., \"player_relation &gt; 0.5\")\n        - target: Node ID to transition to if condition is True\n    npc_state: Current state of the NPC, including conversation data</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    Target node_id if a matching transition is found, None otherwise</p>\n\n<p>Notes:\n    - Transitions are evaluated in order; first match wins\n    - Invalid or failing conditions are skipped with a warning\n    - Uses restricted eval for safety (only allows SAFE_NAMES variables)</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code multiline\">(<span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">transitions</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]]</span>,</span><span class=\"param\">\t<span class=\"n\">npc_state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">narrative_engine</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">session</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NPCConversationState</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"n\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.is_terminal": {"fullname": "narrative_engine.TransitionResolver.is_terminal", "modulename": "narrative_engine", "qualname": "TransitionResolver.is_terminal", "kind": "function", "doc": "<p>Check if a node is terminal (ends the conversation).</p>\n\n<p>A node is terminal if it has no choices and is explicitly marked\nas terminal in the scenario data.</p>\n\n<p>Args:\n    node: The node dictionary to check</p>\n\n<p>Returns:\n    True if the node is terminal, False otherwise</p>\n", "signature": "<span class=\"signature pdoc-code condensed\">(<span class=\"param\"><span class=\"n\">node</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Any</span><span class=\"p\">]</span></span><span class=\"return-annotation\">) -> <span class=\"nb\">bool</span>:</span></span>", "funcdef": "def"}, "pne": {"fullname": "pne", "modulename": "pne", "kind": "module", "doc": "<p>Psychological Narrative Engine - Package Initialization\nAuthor: Jerome Bawa</p>\n\n<p>This package provides a modular dialogue system implementing the Purpose-Output Model\nwith Conversation Containment, Interaction Outcomes, and Terminal Outcomes.</p>\n"}, "pne.LanguageArt": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>Player Dialogue Approaches (Rhetoric)</p>\n", "bases": "enum.Enum"}, "pne.LanguageArt.CHALLENGE": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt.CHALLENGE", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt.CHALLENGE", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;LanguageArt.CHALLENGE: &#x27;challenge&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.LanguageArt.DIPLOMATIC": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt.DIPLOMATIC", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt.DIPLOMATIC", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;LanguageArt.DIPLOMATIC: &#x27;diplomatic&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.LanguageArt.EMPATHETIC": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt.EMPATHETIC", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt.EMPATHETIC", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;LanguageArt.EMPATHETIC: &#x27;empathetic&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.LanguageArt.MANIPULATIVE": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt.MANIPULATIVE", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt.MANIPULATIVE", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;LanguageArt.MANIPULATIVE: &#x27;manipulative&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.LanguageArt.NEUTRAL": {"fullname": "pne.LanguageArt.NEUTRAL", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "LanguageArt.NEUTRAL", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;LanguageArt.NEUTRAL: &#x27;neutral&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.PlayerSkill": {"fullname": "pne.PlayerSkill", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "PlayerSkill", "kind": "class", "doc": "<p>Player's skill proficiencies</p>\n", "bases": "enum.Enum"}, "pne.PlayerSkill.AUTHORITY": {"fullname": "pne.PlayerSkill.AUTHORITY", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "PlayerSkill.AUTHORITY", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;PlayerSkill.AUTHORITY: &#x27;authority&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.PlayerSkill.DIPLOMACY": {"fullname": "pne.PlayerSkill.DIPLOMACY", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "PlayerSkill.DIPLOMACY", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;PlayerSkill.DIPLOMACY: &#x27;diplomacy&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.PlayerSkill.EMPATHY": {"fullname": "pne.PlayerSkill.EMPATHY", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "PlayerSkill.EMPATHY", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;PlayerSkill.EMPATHY: &#x27;empathy&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.PlayerSkill.MANIPULATION": {"fullname": "pne.PlayerSkill.MANIPULATION", "modulename": "pne", "qualname": "PlayerSkill.MANIPULATION", "kind": "variable", "doc": "<p></p>\n", "default_value": "&lt;PlayerSkill.MANIPULATION: &#x27;manipulation&#x27;&gt;"}, "pne.TerminalOutcomeType": {